  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "HOW TO PLAY BIBLICAL\r\n\r\nOBJECTIVE\r\nDestroy your opponent's Altar
    before they destroy yours. Each Altar starts with 30 health.\r\n\r\nTURNS\r\nEach
    turn your mana increases by 1 (max 10). Spend mana to play cards from your hand.\r\n\r\nUNITS\r\nUnits
    can attack enemy units or the opponent's Altar. Units cannot attack the turn
    they are played. You can only attack the Altar if the opponent has no units on
    board.\r\n\r\nCARD TYPES\r\n- Battlecry: Triggers when the card is played\r\n-
    Deathrattle: Triggers when the unit dies\r\n- Scripture: Spell cards with powerful
    effects\r\n\r\nRARITIES\r\n- Legendary (Gold) \u2014 Unique, game-changing cards\r\n-
    Epic (Purple) \u2014 Powerful, impactful cards  \r\n- Rare (Blue) \u2014 Solid,
    reliable cards\r\n- Common (Grey) \u2014 Buildable foundation cards\r\n\r\nWhile
    in game, right click any card to inspect it closely."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: bae2c79e9608bd740b47665290912424, type: 2}
